::Hot Rod::

He layed in his bed. He thought of the last few hours. He had just been
with nice, lovily bot. He was happy. He got up, cleaned up, and walked
out of his room. He thought if he should go see her, or let her be. He
started walking to her lab, maybe he could help her with some work.
